title: CHILLING ADVENTURES OF SABRINA Season 3 Ending Explained + Season 4 Theories!
author: Think Story
comment: Quite possibly my most scuffed intro ever! Hope you guys liked the video and the latest season. Let me know what you thought below 💖🧹🧹
Did anyone else find her cerimony dress and look to be hideous? She looked so stunning at first and than by the end I'm just like...WTF
Hilda's revenge was really satisfying to see 😂😍😘
I feel like the time travel part was such a cop out ... I wish the writers would’ve done something else :(
Am i the only one who likes part 2 better like story wise? I just feel like part 3 is all over the place.
description:
Season 3 of the Chilling Adventures of Sabrina is finally here with lots to breakdown. I recap, review, and explain the ending to part 3 as well as theories for season 4.
